{"tid":356041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有請小鳳姐】住半山億元豪宅 19歲支那女遇電騙破財","createTime":"2017-08-11T18:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T03:48:53.000Z","uid":43189,"like":68,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d22572ebdf352aae8cf278f9adef1dd2c3f11636","tid":356041,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T18:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DXqGflYsOOpjyxB3mLnFOQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/skypost/11JHD001__20170811_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDXqGflYsOOpjyxB3mLnFOQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fskypost%2F11JHD001__20170811_L.jpg&h=a711c389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【晴報專訊】家住半山億元豪宅、父母為內地上市公司董事的一名19歲少女，前天墮電騙陷阱，誤以為自己捲入刑事案，直至按「公安」指示存入4.5萬元「保證金」後才察覺有問題，報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n遇騙19歲少女性郭，為大學生。<span style=\"color: red;\">消息稱，郭的父母均是內地上市公司的股東，父親更是有名的「股壇狙擊手」，身家豐厚。</span>她家住半山梅道1號「The Mayfair」一單位；該豪宅面積逾2,000呎，據報2014年的成交價已達1億，目前更不止此數。<br />\n<br />\n父母為上市公司董事<br />\n<br />\n郭姓少女前天接到一名自稱執法人員的女子來電，電話隨即轉駁到一名「內地公安」，對方指郭涉嫌與一宗刑事案件有關，要求她把「保證金」存入一個內地銀行戶口，以證清白。<br />\n<br />\n郭在「內地公安」連嚇帶騙下會以為真，便按指示存入4.5萬港元。之後她向親友透露事件，才驚悉自己上當受騙，至昨天凌晨零時在住所報警求助。目前警方將案列作「以欺騙手段取得財產」處理，交由灣仔警區刑事調查第8隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，警方上半年共接獲443宗電話騙案舉報，較去年同期增加33宗，損失金額達1.4億元。至7月份，電騙數字再明顯增加，1至24日間已有130宗，平均每日5.4宗，損失合計1,800萬。警方指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">電話騙案逾6成受害人在30歲以下，又有超過3成是內地留學生及來港工作人士。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NKr8N.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNKr8N.gif&h=aabe45d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f8441ce1dd2d7b88d1de69858f82567a5867881","tid":356041,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T18:17:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BD%8F%E5%8D%8A%E5%B1%B1%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85-19%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E9%81%87%E9%9B%BB%E9%A8%99%E7%A0%B4%E8%B2%A1-225043619.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25AE%2585-19%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%2581%2587%25E9%259B%25BB%25E9%25A8%2599%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%25B2%25A1-225043619.html&d=BGzdSWcpVg%2FRzrXWWL2Ys%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d966e943\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BD%8F%E5%8D%8A%E5%B1%B1%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85-19%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E9%81%87%E9%9B%BB%E9%A8%99%E7%A0%B4%E8%B2%A1-225043619.html</a>"},{"pid":"6ba5783a120c6a949f934e78f1980adacf418aa5","tid":356041,"uid":37153,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T18:18:19.000Z","msg":"4萬5幾呎都買唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪當散銀跌左"},{"pid":"9510d1d3d96ee42f67236fdf94f328f4de7c1d86","tid":356041,"uid":111253,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T18:19:27.000Z","msg":"5皮嘢佢老豆當跌咗散子咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dceb54646d00c4b262d5e093dac90834610852","tid":356041,"uid":16528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T18:22:38.000Z","msg":"個女應該唔係個老豆既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb904dde2be095dcf87cdefaa4e6ed69bacd1ede","tid":356041,"uid":36421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T18:23:20.000Z","msg":"先嗰幾皮嘢 應該一日賺既錢都唔止呢個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7d3cb7668ee7ca5dc11aea9d55764fa3c1daf6","tid":356041,"uid":129340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T18:29:00.000Z","msg":"一個月飯錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da8b9b6d709e925bd12f5769b07201d1a10fd30","tid":35